{"tid":1313243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為沙田人 真係建議大家聽日發夢保護好自己","createTime":"2019-07-13T17:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T05:40:39.000Z","uid":278783,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3d472eca4d5da972c9cdd5087c9ea96753ce2789","tid":1313243,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"利申：借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n本人當然唔希望聽日發生咩事，但我建議大家聽日發夢真係多留意身邊既形勢同地理。<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好睇沙田好大，但其實逃跑路線唔多，基本上進出得幾條路線（尤以火車站，沙田政府合署更甚） ，如果對面整路障封埋火車站基本上會比人包抄,加上聽日有好多交通工具改路建議大家唔好太過期望發生起事上黎可以搭車走佬。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹為住左二十幾年沙田既朋友發夢9up<br />\n<br />\n香港人Be water!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829a3195f967377fcf1a51a903d99ce9ba26c0ef","tid":1313243,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:06:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d3c7f98ef9708cecfb90d88d4404237159685012","tid":1313243,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81cea1b9d8f21499cdd68e0c464df6c26ded6b","tid":1313243,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6084669974e112578615f81e51e94e28a20b6d67","tid":1313243,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e788ae140c8d9113f297c1c7c860aeea8ad5d496","tid":1313243,"uid":107447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割席"},{"pid":"0dd708a71f7faf25f23d80e76a9f781ad9329369","tid":1313243,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fd06f821da17867